<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">McDonald’s sued by 52 former franchises, accused of racial discrimination</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/2020/09/01/mcdonalds-franchisees-discrimination-lawsuit/</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">52 former McDonald’s franchisees sue chain for racial discrimination</span></p>
